  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I came over to England in a transport September, 1945, to Southampton.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We arrived at dusk or 10 o'clock at night, about, as I said, 29th or 30th of September.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a double-decker bus waiting for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Stupid things you remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They had to carry the luggage upstairs, because we were all frightened to go upstairs in case the bus topples over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was so [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we finished up in-- in [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Dudley ?] House, Southampton in a hostel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was there about four or six weeks, then we were taken all the way to Scotland, and a little village called Cardross, where I met up the boys who came from Theresienstadt to-- and then on to Windermere.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from Windermere-- when they close Windermere, they all-- they all finished up in this Cardross in this hostel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It's a lovely house, far-- along-- all the way uphill from the village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we began to live a little.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a lovely summer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We used to have two bikes, two bikes between eight boys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So whoever managed to get the bike first-- it was always me-- that's why I broke a leg, and I broke an-- an ankle, and my wrist, and off we went for the day.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when there was any lessons going, I was hardly there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I fell off my bike and we used to sort of go down this hill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And suddenly, a herd of cows appeared in front of you, braked my brake, finished up in the fields.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you know, a  little-- we started-- as I said, we start to live, and we sort of, you know, we were taken to, like, places, to the cinema.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were taken to [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Button ?] Barton.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
